## Enterprise SSO (SAML — one-liner reference)

```
Available on: Team and Enterprise plans only
Use case: B2B SaaS where enterprise customers require SAML SSO
Providers: Okta, Azure AD, Google Workspace, any SAML 2.0 provider

Setup: Dashboard → Auth → SSO Providers → Add provider
Docs: supabase.com/docs/guides/auth/enterprise-sso
```
